mbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://www.adobe.com/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Adobe Creative Cloud","item":"/creativecloud/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Adobe Firefly","item":"/products/firefly/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":4,"name":"Features","item":"/products/firefly/features/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":5,"name":"AI Art Generator","item":"/products/firefly/features/ai-art-generator/"}]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/creativecloud/blocks/firefly-howto/firefly-howto.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/UniversalNav.css"><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"How to generate AI art.","description":"Steps on how to generate AI art","step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 1 Open the AI art generator in Firefly.","text":"To get started, log in to Adobe Firefly with your Adobe ID or create a free account if you don’t have one. Once you’re in, select the Generate Image feature from the Firefly homepage to begin creating."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 2 Generate AI art.","text":"Start by browsing example images and prompts. Click on any example to view variations, or hover over them to see their prompts. Enter your own prompt when you’re ready. For help getting started, get tips on how to write an AI art prompt."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 3 Refine and regenerate artwork.","text":"Fine-tune your prompt for more specific results, or click Generate again to explore different versions. You can also switch up the style, composition, or subject to see how different prompts affect the outcome."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 4 Customize your image.","text":"Once your art image is generated, use the settings panel to adjust style, aspect ratio, color, lighting, and more. Firefly makes it easy to explore new directions without starting from scratch — just update your prompt or tweak the settings."},{"@type":"HowToStep","name":"Step 5 Save and share your AI generated artwork.","text":"Download the image, copy it to your clipboard, or share it with others. You can also submit it to the Firefly gallery to inspire the community. Each piece includes a small label noting it was created with Adobe Firefly."}],"totalTime":"PT5M","tool":[{"@type":"HowToTool","name":"firefly"}]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/editorial-card/editorial-card.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/styles/rounded-corners.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/creativecloud/blocks/firefly-carousel/firefly-carousel.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/accordion/accordion.css"><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[[{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              What is an AI art generator?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"An AI art generator is a type of technology that can create digital images with generative artificial intelligence. Firefly uses text prompts to generate artwork, which can then be customized into a variety of styles. Images can look like pop art, marble sculptures, clay ceramics, or watercolor paintings, just to name a few.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              How does an AI art generator work?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"AI art generators are a type of generative artificial intelligence. Like other types of artificial intelligence, generative AI relies on large datasets to produce the desired result, such as digital artwork, creating something totally new — all triggered by a single text prompt. The current Firefly generative AI model is trained on a dataset from Adobe Stock, openly licensed content, and public domain content where the copyright has expired.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              How do you make AI generated art?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Adobe Firefly is a fast, intuitive way to create AI generated art in a variety of styles. It lets creators produce detailed, stylish images with a text prompt. You can quickly customize your images with other Firefly tools, or fine-tune it even further in Creative Cloud apps like Adobe Photoshop.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Do I own the copyright to AI art generated in Firefly?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Yes, you own the rights to images you create in Firefly, including those generated with generative credits, as outlined in the Adobe terms of use.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Do I need an Adobe Firefly subscription to generate AI art?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"No subscription is required to start — you can create AI generated art with a free Adobe account. Paid plans offer additional features and more generative credits.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              How do I get better results with AI-generated artwork?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"To get better results with AI-generated artwork, use clear text prompts, add reference images, and refine your results through iteration. Start with a simple description of your subject, style, and mood, then adjust keywords to improve composition or detail. You can also click the Prompt Features button in the toolbar and turn on Prompt Enhancement, which automatically expands your text into a more detailed prompt.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Can I generate images in Adobe Firefly using Nano Banana?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Yes. Nano Banana is available as a partner model for image generation in Adobe Firefly. You can access it through the Text to image module by selecting Gemini 2.5 Flash Image from the model dropdown menu.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Is the Adobe Firefly AI art generator free?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"You can start creating AI generated images and artwork in Adobe Firefly for free using a limited number of generative credits. This lets you explore what Firefly can do without committing to a plan. When you're ready for more, you can upgrade to a paid subscription to access additional credits and unlock premium features across Firefly and the broader Creative Cloud ecosystem.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              What makes Adobe Firefly different from other AI art tools?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Adobe Firefly is designed for creators and artists who need brand-safe, commercially ready outputs. It integrates seamlessly with Adobe Creative Cloud and offers powerful customization options that fit any creative workflow. You can also access other leading AI art tools — like GPT Image by OpenAI, FLUX, and NanoBanana — directly from Firefly, so you never have to leave your workspace.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              Are there any limitations when using Adobe Firefly?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"While Adobe Firefly is a powerful AI tool for professional creators, there are a few limitations to keep in mind. Some outputs have maximum resolution limits, and only specific file formats are supported. Highly specific or experimental artistic styles may not be fully achievable. Firefly is constantly evolving, with ongoing improvements to resolution, formats, and style options.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n            \n              What is the best AI art generator?\n            \n          ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The best AI art generators accurately interpret prompts, offer diverse artistic styles, produce high-resolution images, and support commercial use. Adobe Firefly meets these standards by allowing users to generate detailed artwork from text, refine styles, and download professional-quality images. The Firefly model is also designed to be commercially safe, making it suitable for business and creative production use.","@type":"Answer"}}]]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/creativecloud/blocks/firefly-share/firefly-share.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/layout.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/popover.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/profile.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/styles/inline.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/global-footer/global-footer.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/global-navigation/utilities/menu/menu.css"></head>
