      <div class="section" daa-lh="s13">
        <div class="accordion-container seo max-width-12-desktop static-links con-block" data-block-status="loaded" daa-lh="b1|accordion-conta"><div class="descr-list accordion foreground" id="accordion-1" role="presentation"><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-1" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-1" daa-ll="open-1--What is an AI art ge">
            
              What is an AI art generator?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-1" id="accordion-1-content-1" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>An AI art generator is a type of technology that can create digital images with generative artificial intelligence. Firefly uses text prompts to generate artwork, which can then be customized into a variety of styles. Images can look like pop art, marble sculptures, clay ceramics, or watercolor paintings, just to name a few.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-2" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-2" daa-ll="open-2--How does an AI art g">
            
              How does an AI art generator work?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-2" id="accordion-1-content-2" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>AI art generators are a type of generative artificial intelligence. Like other types of artificial intelligence, generative AI relies on large datasets to produce the desired result, such as digital artwork, creating something totally new — all triggered by a single text prompt. The current Firefly generative AI model is trained on a dataset from Adobe Stock, openly licensed content, and public domain content where the copyright has expired.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-3" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-3" daa-ll="open-3--How do you make AI g">
            
              How do you make AI generated art?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-3" id="accordion-1-content-3" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Adobe Firefly is a fast, intuitive way to create AI generated art in a variety of styles. It lets creators produce detailed, stylish images with a text prompt. You can quickly customize your images with other Firefly tools, or fine-tune it even further in Creative Cloud apps like Adobe Photoshop.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-4" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-4" daa-ll="open-4--Do I own the copyrig">
            
              Do I own the copyright to AI art generated in Firefly?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-4" id="accordion-1-content-4" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, you own the rights to images you create in Firefly, including those generated with generative credits, as outlined in the Adobe terms of use.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-5" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-5" daa-ll="open-5--Do I need an Adobe F">
            
              Do I need an Adobe Firefly subscription to generate AI art?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>No subscription is required to start — you can create AI generated art with a free Adobe account. Paid plans offer additional features and more <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/firefly/web/get-started/learn-the-basics/generative-credits-overview.html" daa-ll="generative credits-6--Do I need an Adobe F">generative credits</a>.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-6" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-6" daa-ll="open-6--How do I get better ">
            
              How do I get better results with AI-generated artwork?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-6" id="accordion-1-content-6" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>
              <p>To get better results with AI-generated artwork, use clear text prompts, add reference images, and refine your results through iteration. Start with a simple description of your subject, style, and mood, then adjust keywords to improve composition or detail. You can also click the Prompt Features button in the toolbar and turn on Prompt Enhancement, which automatically expands your text into a more detailed prompt.</p>
              <p>Uploading a sketch or photo can help guide structure and color, leading to more accurate outputs. With Adobe Firefly’s AI art generator, you can combine prompts and references, generate multiple variations, and fine-tune your artwork until it matches your creative vision.</p>
            </div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-7" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-7" daa-ll="open-7--Can I generate image">
            
              Can I generate images in Adobe Firefly using Nano Banana?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-7" id="accordion-1-content-7" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes. Nano Banana is available as a partner model for image generation in Adobe Firefly. You can access it through the Text to image module by selecting Gemini 2.5 Flash Image from the model dropdown menu.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-8" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-8" daa-ll="open-8--Is the Adobe Firefly">
            
              Is the Adobe Firefly AI art generator free?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-8" id="accordion-1-content-8" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>You can start creating AI generated images and artwork in Adobe Firefly for free using a limited number of generative credits. This lets you explore what Firefly can do without committing to a plan. When you're ready for more, you can upgrade to a paid subscription to access additional credits and unlock premium features across Firefly and the broader Creative Cloud ecosystem.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-9" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-9" daa-ll="open-9--What makes Adobe Fir">
            
              What makes Adobe Firefly different from other AI art tools?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-9" id="accordion-1-content-9" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Adobe Firefly is designed for creators and artists who need brand-safe, commercially ready outputs. It integrates seamlessly with Adobe Creative Cloud and offers powerful customization options that fit any creative workflow. You can also access other leading AI art tools — like GPT Image by OpenAI, FLUX, and NanoBanana — directly from Firefly, so you never have to leave your workspace.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-10" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-10" daa-ll="open-10--Are there any limita">
            
              Are there any limitations when using Adobe Firefly?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-10" id="accordion-1-content-10" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>While Adobe Firefly is a powerful AI tool for professional creators, there are a few limitations to keep in mind. Some outputs have maximum resolution limits, and only specific file formats are supported. Highly specific or experimental artistic styles may not be fully achievable. Firefly is constantly evolving, with ongoing improvements to resolution, formats, and style options.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-11" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-11" daa-ll="open-11--What is the best AI ">
            
              What is the best AI art generator?
            
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-11" id="accordion-1-content-11" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The best AI art generators accurately interpret prompts, offer diverse artistic styles, produce high-resolution images, and support commercial use. Adobe Firefly meets these standards by allowing users to generate detailed artwork from text, refine styles, and download professional-quality images. The Firefly model is also designed to be commercially safe, making it suitable for business and creative production use.</div></div></div></div>
      </div>
